00:01:29,979 --> 00:01:32,979
[Episode 5]

4
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:42,120
Why did you pour the tea?

5
00:01:45,920 --> 00:01:46,600
Follow me.

6
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:14,200
Master.

7
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:16,760
Why don't you allow Eleven to go enjoy the music?

8
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:18,560
It's rare to hear the music played by musicians from Nanxiao.

9
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:24,360
She poured a pot of tea.

10
00:02:24,920 --> 00:02:26,079
I'm punishing her by asking her to copy tea names.

11
00:02:36,720 --> 00:02:37,360
Master.

12
00:02:38,079 --> 00:02:40,079
Are you teasing her

13
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:41,400
because she can't speak?

14
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:44,160
Famous tea is expensive.

15
00:02:44,320 --> 00:02:45,560
But she wasted it at will.

16
00:02:45,880 --> 00:02:46,680
Shouldn't she be punished?

17
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:11,880
Do you feel grieved?

18
00:03:15,200 --> 00:03:17,360
You should know the value of a cup of tea

19
00:03:17,640 --> 00:03:18,840
worth days of,

20
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:20,520
even a month of food for common people.

21
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:22,800
You like to drink tea.

22
00:03:22,920 --> 00:03:23,800
So I bought you tea.

23
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:25,920
But I don't want you to be arrogant

24
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:27,640
and unaware of how hard common people's life is.

25
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:31,880
You should cultivate virtue by staying thrift.

26
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,640
You are the future Crown Princess.

27
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,040
You should set an example.

28
00:03:38,480 --> 00:03:39,040
What's wrong?

29
00:03:54,160 --> 00:03:55,520
As the junior Prince of Nanchen's disciple,

30
00:03:55,600 --> 00:03:59,080
I should remember it, but it has nothing to do with the name of Crown Princess.

31
00:04:14,600 --> 00:04:16,920
I'm willing to be punished.

32
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:27,280
Most of the tea comes from Nanxiao

33
00:04:27,760 --> 00:04:28,880
and the Jiduo Kingdom.

34
00:04:30,200 --> 00:04:31,920
I handled that from Jiduo.

35
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:32,880
Wait. Let me find it out.

36
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:35,240
This one.

37
00:04:37,680 --> 00:04:38,920
Yes, that's it.

38
00:04:38,960 --> 00:04:39,880
Look, there're words on it.

39
00:04:39,880 --> 00:04:41,120
Abstruse writing.

40
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:44,120
But it says cinnamon.

41
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:46,560
Cinnamon is not tea?

42
00:04:48,520 --> 00:04:50,120
Then where's the tea?

43
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:59,240
When did you learn Jiduo's language?

44
00:05:00,280 --> 00:05:01,320
When I went to the temple

45
00:05:01,320 --> 00:05:02,440
to pray for you these two years,

46
00:05:02,960 --> 00:05:04,080
I met monks from

47
00:05:04,080 --> 00:05:04,640
the Jiduo Kingdom

48
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:05,560
and I learned it from them.

49
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:07,560
Since you can learn their language,

50
00:05:07,760 --> 00:05:08,960
you must go to the temple very frequently.

51
00:05:10,520 --> 00:05:11,840
I would go there when I miss you all.

52
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:15,840
No wonder Xie Yun always became wordy

53
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:17,080
when he went to the battlefield.

54
00:05:17,240 --> 00:05:18,880
He said there was a little sister

55
00:05:18,880 --> 00:05:19,760
waiting for us at home

56
00:05:19,840 --> 00:05:21,040
and we should not lose our lives.

57
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:24,600
He knows you best.

58
00:05:26,660 --> 00:05:29,620
[Nanchen Royal Mansion]

59
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:37,440
The four of them are guards from the imperial palace.

60
00:05:37,440 --> 00:05:38,640
They follow to protect me.

61
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:42,680
Zhou Tianxing.

62
00:05:42,760 --> 00:05:43,760
Feng Qiao.

63
00:05:43,960 --> 00:05:45,159
Greetings, Your Highness.

64
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:48,080
I know you.

65
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:49,960
You are a meritorious general following the junior Prince of Nanchen

66
00:05:49,960 --> 00:05:51,800
to suppress the Six-garrison Rebellion.

67
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:54,800
Where is my uncle?

68
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:56,560
