69
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:58,040
He left us to entertain Your Highness.

70
00:05:59,840 --> 00:06:01,720
Uncle really loves soldiers as if they were his children.

71
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:03,000
It seems he is going to spend

72
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:03,880
the New Year's Eve with generals and soldiers.

73
00:06:13,400 --> 00:06:15,120
Is there any scenic place

74
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:16,360
in his mansion?

75
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:21,800
I don't want her

76
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:23,440
to feel chained when we meet for the first time.

77
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:25,720
There is a garden

78
00:06:25,960 --> 00:06:27,120
with pavilion, pond and beautiful scenery.

79
00:06:27,320 --> 00:06:28,520
Shiyi often practices instrument there.

80
00:06:30,840 --> 00:06:31,840
Then I'll go there.

81
00:06:48,840 --> 00:06:49,560
People in the mansion

82
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:50,760
are talking about the Prince of Guangling.

83
00:06:50,880 --> 00:06:52,400
They said he has been good-looking since he was a child

84
00:06:52,400 --> 00:06:53,200
and he is famous outside the palace.

85
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:54,880
What they said is true.

86
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:56,440
He is a quite handsome man.

87
00:06:58,480 --> 00:07:00,120
Why should we judge people by appearance?

88
00:07:00,960 --> 00:07:03,080
Well, being good-looking is definitely not a disadvantage.

89
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:06,160
A hundred years ago, the emperor of Xiyan Kingdom,

90
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:07,040
Murong Chong,

91
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:09,000
was imprisoned as a toy-boy and suffered humiliation

92
00:07:09,400 --> 00:07:11,000
when he was young

93
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:12,040
because he looked even better than women.

94
00:07:13,080 --> 00:07:14,280
Isn't it all because of his appearance?

95
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:17,360
It was really a pity for you

96
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:18,600
to lose ability to speak these years.

97
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:24,440
No matter he is your future husband

98
00:07:24,520 --> 00:07:25,520
or just a guest from afar,

99
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:27,560
you should show hospitality.

100
00:07:29,320 --> 00:07:31,120
You are more like the descendant from the Cui family than I am.

101
00:07:32,640 --> 00:07:33,520
How I wish

102
00:07:35,080 --> 00:07:35,840
you were me.

103
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:23,960
Greetings, Your Highness.

104
00:08:52,800 --> 00:08:53,360
Your Highness.

105
00:08:59,120 --> 00:09:00,240
We're not in the Central State.

106
00:09:00,360 --> 00:09:01,080
