107
00:09:01,520 --> 00:09:02,240
Get up.

108
00:09:03,160 --> 00:09:04,040
Thank you, Your Highness.

109
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:18,280
I finally don't need to

110
00:09:18,280 --> 00:09:19,200
see you through portrait.

111
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:25,960
In the Central State, I often heard that

112
00:09:25,960 --> 00:09:27,600
Nanchen Royal Mansion is magnificent.

113
00:09:27,880 --> 00:09:29,160
But I didn't take it seriouly.

114
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:31,920
Now when I'm here,

115
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:33,360
I realize it is true.

116
00:09:35,540 --> 00:09:37,180
Your Highness, don't be misled by the public.

117
00:09:38,220 --> 00:09:39,020
For what?

118
00:09:40,420 --> 00:09:42,500
My master is not extravagant.

119
00:09:43,220 --> 00:09:44,980
But as the prince guarding the borders,

120
00:09:45,220 --> 00:09:46,780
his residence must be magnificent

121
00:09:47,100 --> 00:09:48,300
to win the hearts of the people.

122
00:09:49,340 --> 00:09:50,780
You are afraid that I will think

123
00:09:50,860 --> 00:09:52,220
he is disloyal like other princes?

124
00:09:53,060 --> 00:09:54,300
I dare not think so.

125
00:09:55,940 --> 00:09:58,540
I'm not that blind and stupid.

126
00:09:59,020 --> 00:10:00,340
Other royal families and fierce generals

127
00:10:00,660 --> 00:10:01,740
might be rebellious

128
00:10:01,740 --> 00:10:02,900
or wait for an opportunity

129
00:10:03,020 --> 00:10:04,380
to rebel

130
00:10:04,460 --> 00:10:05,460
when they take control of

131
00:10:05,580 --> 00:10:07,300
thousands of military soldiers.

132
00:10:07,380 --> 00:10:09,220
But he won't.

133
00:10:09,460 --> 00:10:11,980
Beichen is so lucky to have him.

134
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:21,380
It's against the rules.

135
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:27,680
Are you all right?

136
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:29,960
I'm fine.

137
00:10:30,880 --> 00:10:32,000
I'm just caring about you.

138
00:10:32,400 --> 00:10:33,000
Show me your hand.

139
00:10:33,680 --> 00:10:34,760
There are doctors in the mansion.

140
00:10:34,920 --> 00:10:35,760
I'll see them by myself.

141
00:10:43,760 --> 00:10:44,760
Send an imperial doctor to check her hand.

142
00:10:44,760 --> 00:10:45,480
Now!

143
00:10:45,880 --> 00:10:46,360
Yes.

144
00:10:57,820 --> 00:10:59,420
Why did you get hurt for the first time you met him?

145
00:10:59,540 --> 00:11:00,860
