146
00:11:02,060 --> 00:11:03,700
He was closely surrounded by

147
00:11:03,700 --> 00:11:04,540
four guards with knives.

148
00:11:05,020 --> 00:11:06,660
Even after the maids and chamberlains had left,

149
00:11:06,820 --> 00:11:07,780
they guarded him also.

150
00:11:08,420 --> 00:11:09,780
Is he afraid there would be

151
00:11:09,780 --> 00:11:10,980
assassins even in Nanchen Royal Mansion?

152
00:11:12,540 --> 00:11:13,940
That's the strange point.

153
00:11:23,340 --> 00:11:23,860
Your Highness.

154
00:11:23,860 --> 00:11:24,580
How is she?

155
00:11:25,220 --> 00:11:27,140
Miss Cui is all right. Don't worry.

156
00:11:29,580 --> 00:11:30,620
As soon as I saw her...

157
00:11:35,780 --> 00:11:37,220
I had a mood

158
00:11:37,380 --> 00:11:38,300
that I won't understand.

159
00:11:39,980 --> 00:11:41,340
Although I'm have been castrated,

160
00:11:42,060 --> 00:11:43,140
I'm still a human.

161
00:11:44,020 --> 00:11:46,460
Since I'm human, I have emotions.

162
00:11:50,580 --> 00:11:51,900
She is different from that on the portrait.

163
00:11:53,140 --> 00:11:54,980
She won't stand still to let me gaze at her.

164
00:12:00,780 --> 00:12:01,700
She will be afraid

165
00:12:02,620 --> 00:12:03,700
and then get away from me.

166
00:12:07,300 --> 00:12:08,620
Uncle is not in the mansion.

167
00:12:09,260 --> 00:12:11,420
I have to find a good reason to see him.

168
00:12:24,700 --> 00:12:25,980
Today is your birthday.

169
00:12:26,140 --> 00:12:27,060
What's your wish?

170
00:12:31,460 --> 00:12:32,860
Let me tell you what gifts I've prepared for you.

171
00:12:34,020 --> 00:12:34,980
Your Highness is a guest.

172
00:12:35,300 --> 00:12:36,140
No need to spend money on me.

173
00:12:39,740 --> 00:12:40,660
Greetings, Your Highness.

174
00:12:41,140 --> 00:12:42,620
You two generals finally came.

175
00:12:43,780 --> 00:12:44,620
Thank you, Your Highness.

176
00:12:45,940 --> 00:12:47,700
Your Highness, what can we do for you?

177
00:12:48,340 --> 00:12:49,820
I've prepared good wine and food.

178
00:12:49,820 --> 00:12:51,620
I want to go to the army barracks with you

179
00:12:51,700 --> 00:12:52,900
to celebrate Shiyi's birthday.

180
00:12:58,300 --> 00:13:00,260
It feels like home in the royal mansion.

181
00:13:00,700 --> 00:13:01,700
I think

182
00:13:04,540 --> 00:13:06,460
Shiyi must want to celebrate her birthday

183
00:13:06,500 --> 00:13:07,580
with her family.

184
00:13:07,900 --> 00:13:09,460
But the Royal Army has strict rules.

185
00:13:09,500 --> 00:13:10,500
Outsiders are not allowed to enter the camp without permission.

186
00:13:11,180 --> 00:13:12,300
Am I an outsider?

187
00:13:13,500 --> 00:13:15,500
I mean those without military status.

188
00:13:19,100 --> 00:13:20,540
What if I have an imperial edict

189
00:13:20,700 --> 00:13:22,780
to reward the army on behalf of His Majesty?

190
00:13:29,780 --> 00:13:30,620
In this case,

191
00:13:30,940 --> 00:13:31,940
I'll make an arrangement right now.

192
00:13:43,060 --> 00:13:44,740
I just wanted to give you a birthday present.

193
00:13:46,860 --> 00:13:48,300
I didn't know you have an edict.

194
00:13:48,500 --> 00:13:50,740
I'm sorry for embarrassing you.

195
00:13:52,140 --> 00:13:52,700
Never mind.

196
00:13:53,340 --> 00:13:54,460
It's okay because it is you.

197
00:14:10,260 --> 00:14:10,820
Your Highness.

198
00:14:11,420 --> 00:14:13,340
