199
00:14:17,740 --> 00:14:18,340
Master.

200
00:14:19,140 --> 00:14:20,140
Eleven comes.

201
00:14:21,620 --> 00:14:22,620
Isn't she in the mansion?

202
00:14:23,820 --> 00:14:25,340
The Prince of Guangling brought her here.

203
00:14:25,540 --> 00:14:27,460
He said he wanted to hold a birthday party for her

204
00:14:27,500 --> 00:14:28,420
