205
00:14:28,420 --> 00:14:29,980
to reward the army on behalf of His Majesty.

206
00:14:32,940 --> 00:14:33,780
Let's go and welcome them.

207
00:14:37,460 --> 00:14:38,060
Uncle.

208
00:14:39,300 --> 00:14:39,980
Zixing.

209
00:14:46,060 --> 00:14:46,940
Are you injured?

210
00:14:49,980 --> 00:14:52,340
Xie Yun, take Eleven to see the military doctor.

211
00:14:52,700 --> 00:14:53,220
Yes.

212
00:15:01,860 --> 00:15:02,540
Zixing.

213
00:15:02,780 --> 00:15:03,820
Take a break in the tent.

214
00:15:04,300 --> 00:15:04,860
No hurry.

215
00:15:05,420 --> 00:15:07,100
It's a rare opportunity for me to enter the army barracks.

216
00:15:08,060 --> 00:15:09,580
I wonder if you are free

217
00:15:09,740 --> 00:15:10,860
to show me around.

218
00:15:12,180 --> 00:15:12,780
All right.

219
00:15:13,380 --> 00:15:14,100
Come with me.

220
00:15:21,710 --> 00:15:22,740
Show me your hand.

221
00:15:25,120 --> 00:15:26,680
Master would be worried

222
00:15:26,680 --> 00:15:27,720
if the military doctor didn't check your hand.

223
00:15:28,100 --> 00:15:28,940
Although imperial doctors

224
00:15:28,940 --> 00:15:30,700
have high official titles and read a lot,

225
00:15:31,060 --> 00:15:32,300
they have less experience than

226
00:15:32,900 --> 00:15:34,220
our military doctors.

227
00:15:35,340 --> 00:15:36,420
I'm flattered.

228
00:15:38,380 --> 00:15:39,540
They have already used

229
00:15:39,580 --> 00:15:40,620
good medicine for treating wound.

230
00:15:41,060 --> 00:15:42,620
But I have

231
00:15:42,620 --> 00:15:43,740
folk prescription

232
00:15:44,420 --> 00:15:45,300
which is better than this medicine.

233
00:15:46,660 --> 00:15:47,500
I'll get it right away.

234
00:15:56,140 --> 00:15:57,300
How did he treat you?

235
00:15:59,940 --> 00:16:00,940
With courtesy and integrity.

236
00:16:02,300 --> 00:16:03,140
You are shy.

237
00:16:05,020 --> 00:16:06,220
I've brought Tusu Wine.

238
00:16:07,820 --> 00:16:08,420
Okay.

239
00:16:09,020 --> 00:16:09,860
Since you don't want to say,

240
00:16:10,820 --> 00:16:11,500
