Be careful.

242
00:16:18,940 --> 00:16:19,740
Place everything well.

243
00:16:19,740 --> 00:16:20,100
Yes.

244
00:16:20,220 --> 00:16:20,540
Yes.

245
00:16:24,500 --> 00:16:25,340
It smells good.

246
00:16:27,700 --> 00:16:28,780
It's all your favorite dishes.

247
00:16:33,540 --> 00:16:35,260
Master, I've brought Tusu.

248
00:16:36,300 --> 00:16:37,220
Tusu?

249
00:16:38,980 --> 00:16:39,980
Dinner prepared tonight

250
00:16:39,980 --> 00:16:41,180
looks a little shabbier

251
00:16:41,660 --> 00:16:43,080
