252
00:16:44,540 --> 00:16:45,940
I'll kill some fat sheep.

253
00:16:46,900 --> 00:16:47,380
Give me a knife.

254
00:16:48,340 --> 00:16:49,020
Here.

255
00:17:02,819 --> 00:17:03,859
This cup of Tusu

256
00:17:04,420 --> 00:17:05,660
is for our guest from afar,

257
00:17:06,900 --> 00:17:07,540
Zixing.

258
00:17:11,380 --> 00:17:12,140
Thank you, Uncle.

259
00:17:13,540 --> 00:17:14,700
I also take this cup of wine

260
00:17:15,180 --> 00:17:17,339
as a toast to all of you on behalf of His Majesty.

261
00:17:17,900 --> 00:17:19,579
With a general who can win every battle,

262
00:17:19,980 --> 00:17:21,980
the emperor doesn't have to build the Great Wall.

263
00:17:27,100 --> 00:17:28,540
Thank you, Your Majesty.

264
00:17:28,540 --> 00:17:30,140
Thank you, Your Highness.

