00:18:58,100 --> 00:19:00,340
Finally, I want to say that

279
00:19:02,580 --> 00:19:04,540
today's Eleven's birthday.

280
00:19:05,540 --> 00:19:06,300
I hope

281
00:19:06,300 --> 00:19:07,260
she could be happy every day here.

282
00:19:13,360 --> 00:19:13,960
Eleven.

283
00:19:14,920 --> 00:19:15,600
